casebody.data:
No. 397,

Misc.

Vignera v. New York. Robert S. Rif kind for petitioner. William I. Siegel for respondent.

Ct. App. N. Y. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket and set for oral argument immediately following No. 419, Mise.
